Text: Holiday Cocktail Party the Penns Dec th nsf Elizabeth and I will be having a holiday cocktail party semiformal on December th at our house after PM Bring a date and your favorite libation We will be having plenty of appetizers JellO Shots and other beverages Directions Take Sholls Ferry Rd West Turn Left the th Light There is a day care center on the corner Turn Right at the Stop Sign onto Hawks Beard Rd Turn left into the Summer Creek Apartments We are in the middle of the complex upstairs in SW Hawks Beard Rd Tigard OR Hope to see some of you there Penn
